A tangible impact on future policy that has emerged recently is that the whistle blower at Mid Staffs, A&amp;amp;E Consultant Chris Turner, heard about our project and has joined our Steering Group and initiated the marketing group to help us engage with policy makers and others to make a difference to the way ethical decisions are being made right now by the medical community. 

